   WITH: MILENNIUM DISNEY -- For most of us, welcoming the new
millennium will be a one-night affair, whether decadent or
down-home. But for the folks at Disney, who never do anything less
than over the top, welcoming the new age is a 457-night affair. And
it's already begun. (Walker, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
