   TRAVEL-GROVEPARK _ ASHEVILLE, Ga. _ Asheville's Grove Park Inn
Resort comes through for those seeking an escape in a big way,
especially now that it's all dressed up for the holidays. In
near-oxymoronic fashion, this huge cold-stone structure draws
visitors into its vast spaces, then soothes and warms them
individually with its human stamp on natural elements _ stone,
tile, wood, fiber and the lines of pure and simple art. (Langhenry,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). with Photos and Layout.
</P>
