<P>
   SEVENSISTERS-INN _ OCALA, Fla. _ The Seven Sisters Inn is what
you wish your grandmother's house had been, and so much more. Built
in 1888, it was purchased by husband-and-wife innkeepers Ken Oden
and Bonnie Moorehardt in 1989 and has since been restored to
something better than its 19th-century elegance. Box at bottom of
file. (Park, Palm Beach Post). MOVED.
</P>
