<P>
   FIREHOUSE-SALSA (San Antonio) _ Firefighters in this South Texas
city may find the five-alarm fire right at home. In a tradition
that has spanned decades, the shifts at San Antonio fire stations
are likely to begin in the kitchen, concocting various degrees of
salsa. The recipes are being compiled in a new cookbook, ``San
Antonio Firehouse Salsa.'' By MARO ROBBINS.
