<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-24 12:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0159 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e BC-MOVIE-END-BOS &LR;      11-24 0488
