<P>
   RUSSIAN-NUKES (Washington) _ A small group of U.S. and Russian
military officers won't be doing much cork-popping on New Year's
Eve as the new millenium nears at midnight. Instead, they will be
guarding against the end of the world. By ERIC ROSENBERG.
