 Wednesday, Nov. 24, 1999   Editors  
   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service has filed or will file the following for
Thursday, Friday and Sunday. If you have questions, please call
Susie McBee or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920.
</P>
<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Adds: SCOTUS-WHISTLE; CLINTON-VIEQUES; TEXASA&AMP;M-VIGIL;
GIANT-MARTINI; FBC-A&AMP;M-TEXAS; and FBN-COWBOYS.)
