9-by-13-inch pan. The one she sampled was topped with sliced
strawberries. The cook, who is from Wisconsin, refuses to share the
recipe.
</P>
<P>
   Cesareo Lopez of Fort Worth would like a recipe for
watermelon-rind candy. She had such a recipe years ago but has
misplaced it.
</P>
<P>
   Joanna Scalf of Springtown, Texas, would like a recipe for
sherry wine sauce like the one that the Bay Street restaurants used
to serve.
</P>
<P>
   Peg Shocklee would like a recipe that once appeared on the Cream
Corn Starch box for Boston cream filling.  &QL;
