</P>
<P>
   Photoloft.com &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ALL OF THE ABOVE &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Bungo.com &QL;
</P>
<P>
   eCircles.com &QL;
</P>
<P>
   MagicalDesk.com &QL;
</P>
<P>
   MyFamily.com &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Visto.com  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ALL OF THE ABOVE, PLUS APPLICATIONS LIKE WORD-PROCESSING
PROGRAMS
</P>
