<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-24 20:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0789 &Cx1f; tth-z
r a BC-IMMUNE-DISEASE-SPI &LR;      11-24 1736
