NAKED-POLICE _ At least twice in the past six months, undercover
Mesa police officers have gotten naked to convince massage parlor
prostitution suspects that they aren't really cops. Mesa's
unwritten policy giving officers the go-ahead to disrobe and allow
themselves to be touched, short of sex, goes further than any law
enforcement agency in metro Phoenix, and most agencies across the
nation. By ROBBIE SHERWOOD. Story will move in the ``A'' category. &QL;
