   &QL; 
 &UR; RENDERMAN _  &LR; When people hear ``Pixar,'' Woody, Buzz Lightyear,
Flik and a host of other likable characters from the company's
bubbly animated films inevitably spring to mind. But there's
another name in the animation house's repertoire that will never
rescue a kidnapped toy or lead an ant colony's rebellion, although
``he'' plays a key role in all of Pixar's movies and shorts. By
KELLY ZITO &QL;
